  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top: 0px; margin-right: 5px; border-right: 0px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-left: 5px; border-top: 0px; margin-right: 5px; border-right: 0px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t刘天王演戏与官员扫街</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;All the world's a stage, and all the men and women merely just players.</p>\n<p>\n\tThey have their exits and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/entrance\" target=\"_blank\">entrances</a>,</p>\n<p>\n\tand one man in his time plays many parts.&quot; - a monologue from William Shakespeare's As You Like it.</p>\n<p>\n\tStreet News Agency Report 1：</p>\n<p>\n\tDays ago, someone saw Andy Lau playing an immigrant worker in a street for a new film.<br />\n\tThe worker, also a father who lost his son, was pasting a &quot;person search&quot; leaflet on the walls unauthorisedly.<br />\n\tUnexpectedly, none aware that this <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sloppy\" target=\"_blank\">sloppy</a> worker was played by the smart Andy Lau. Even the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/omnipotent\" target=\"_blank\">omnipotent</a> city-managment officials didn't notice that it was a scene of a film shooting, but to expel the Actors King forcefully, which makes the scene seems authentically.</p>\n<p>\n\tStreet News Agency Report 2:<br />\n\tWhen many officials ride the trend going out of the magnificent building to clean up the street, there are always chance meet for the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/candid\" target=\"_blank\">candid</a> citizens who pass tea, cigarettes, even hot towels to them.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t- In your opinion, how to play your role in the stage of the world?</p>\n<p>\n\t- Andy Lau and these officials, who has the higher show-off skills?</p>\n<p>\n\t- DIY topic</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAs William Shakespeare said all the men and women are players of the world. The level of acting skills doesn't matter but to catch the timing to show off yourself.</p>\n<p>\n\tEven though these officials haven't been professionally directed for film, however, they are also heavenly-king level's actors as Andy Lau.</p>\n<p>\n\tBut the difference between them is that Andy Lau is searching for real life in the perspective of art, while these officials are looking for artistic flavour in real life.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/903094/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p><br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p614554/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p614554\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615236/\">5岁男孩脑癌去世 蜘蛛侠等超级英雄送葬</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p614768/\">20几岁的你需要明白了：生活其实不容易</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615205/\">迪拜遍地豪车遭遗弃 车主负债出逃</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615089/\">小贝长子咖啡店打零工 不做啃老富二代</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http